job.title: Entry Level Software Engineer
job.description: Responsibilities Substantial day-to-day coding, performing profiling, optimizing, and general troubleshooting. Engage in technical planning, design, and code reviews. Participate with other engineers to help plan the company’s long-term engineering roadmap and help identify improvement areas. Qualifications A bachelor's degree or higher in computer science, electrical engineering, or related field. Fluency in one or more general purposes programming languages including but not limited to: Java, C/C++, C#, Python, Objective-C. 3+ years of programming experience. Strong passion for programming. Solid and creative problem-solving skills. Excellent communication skills, both written and verbal. Ability to work in a fast-paced environment. Benefits: Dental insurance, flexible schedule, health insurance, paid time off, referral program, vision insurance, life insurance Job location: 3120 139th Avenue Southeast Suite 500 Bellevue, WA 98005
